4dcd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/094625_a543e98b981b7e6066926e1d61e0e99c.png</a></blockquote><br />\nMikrotik早幾星期都patch左"},{"pid":"8c9cf700fb452bf1fd9ca4d7a319d617acf01e71","tid":438110,"uid":33835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔單只係Android同Linux，Windows同Mac都有事，全世界都有事。講清楚D，唔係又一班玻璃心衝出黎話你係hater。<br />\n<br />\n不過Microsoft已經出左patch。Apple 好似未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 上有https嘅網站應該唔受影響。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有影響， 因為佢會剝離左個 ssl <br />\n令你 redirect 去左 非 https 既網站<br />\n除非你一日到黑睇住個browser 有冇把鎖<br />\n或者果個網站完全停用非 https 接點<br />\n否則你都有機會曝露哂你d 野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢段 YouTube有提到要視乎番個網站既 config"},{"pid":"d24d16340c1662d557bec0f6f453ff245507b8b5","tid":438110,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Unifi 第一時間出左 Firmware 來 Patch ...<br />\n<br />\n記得前排係硬件台介紹 Unifi 比個做 Networking 笑我話做細 Distributor, 真係得淡笑 ...<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/094625_a543e98b981b7e6066926e1d61e0e99c.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F094625_a543e98b981b7e6066926e1d61e0e99c.png&d=Uv8CczrRkfOF72xqJBGoNxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b714dcd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/094625_a543e98b981b7e6066926e1d61e0e99c.png</a></blockquote><br />\nMikrotik早幾星期都patch左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前一排我介紹 Unifi 同 Mikrotik, 有個做 Networking 大神話聽都冇聽過喔 ...<br />\n<br />\n仲有個話我做細 Distributor, 賣雜牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係想知佢邊間公司, 好有興趣認識下佢人事部個 Training Manager, Royalty Training 做得非常到位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似 Apple 咁, 覺得係佢公司做是一種榮耀 ... 當正間公司係佢自己咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我一直都冇叫過人同我買 Unifi 同 Mirkotik, 真係唔知點解有人覺得我是做 Distributor ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/101048_a9024520cb77cdb7ab50f9ca1546355c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F101048_a9024520cb77cdb7ab50f9ca1546355c.png&h=bd402075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/100842_3be37366d3612ebdde2e059a0a9b76e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F100842_3be37366d3612ebdde2e059a0a9b76e5.png&h=1dcc53f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f9d7c44801fd592d68e1660850cc322e2974a2","tid":438110,"uid":13082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"Linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc8cf3325ad1243521b8c1a565c008b7bd1ae8d","tid":438110,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔單只係Android同Linux，Windows同Mac都有事，全世界都有事。講清楚D，唔係又一班玻璃心衝出黎話你係hater。<br />\n<br />\n不過Microsoft已經出左patch。Apple 好似未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 上有https嘅網站應該唔受影響。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有影響， 因為佢會剝離左個 ssl <br />\n令你 redirect 去左 非 https 既網站<br />\n除非你一日到黑睇住個browser 有冇把鎖<br />\n或者果個網站完全停用非 https 接點<br />\n否則你都有機會曝露哂你d 野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYou are right <img src=\"/assets/face